						<summary>

						<p>This inscription records a gift of 50 sheep for a perpetual lamp to the temple of Piṇakkaṟukku Mahādēva at Malaiyaḍikkuṟichi, a southern hamlet of Śri Parāntaka chaturvēdimaṅgalam, a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēyam</hi> in Āri-nāḍu by Veḷḷāḷaṉ Paṭṭaṉ of Peruṅgulai in Sōṇāḍu. </p>						

						</summary>
